Configure Tailwind CSS v4 theme for the Astro project.

Working directory: /Users/so/MyWorkSpace/personal/care-inomi/.worktrees/feature/initial-setup

Read the current src/styles/global.css and update it with the following Tailwind v4 @theme configuration:

```css
@import "tailwindcss";
@import "@fontsource/noto-sans-jp/400.css";
@import "@fontsource/noto-sans-jp/700.css";

@theme {
  /* Colors - Primary (Sakura) */
  --color-sakura-50: oklch(0.98 0.01 350);
  --color-sakura-100: oklch(0.96 0.03 350);
  --color-sakura-200: oklch(0.93 0.05 350);
  --color-sakura-300: oklch(0.89 0.08 350);
  --color-sakura-400: oklch(0.85 0.10 350);
  --color-sakura-500: oklch(0.80 0.12 350);
  --color-sakura-600: oklch(0.65 0.12 350);
  --color-sakura-700: oklch(0.50 0.10 350);
  --color-sakura-800: oklch(0.40 0.08 350);
  --color-sakura-900: oklch(0.30 0.05 350);

  /* Colors - Neutral */
  --color-neutral-50: oklch(0.98 0 0);
  --color-neutral-100: oklch(0.96 0 0);
  --color-neutral-200: oklch(0.92 0 0);
  --color-neutral-300: oklch(0.87 0 0);
  --color-neutral-400: oklch(0.70 0 0);
  --color-neutral-500: oklch(0.55 0 0);
  --color-neutral-600: oklch(0.45 0 0);
  --color-neutral-700: oklch(0.35 0 0);
  --color-neutral-800: oklch(0.25 0 0);
  --color-neutral-900: oklch(0.15 0 0);

  /* Typography */
  --font-heading: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
  --font-body: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
  --font-sans: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;

  /* Spacing */
  --container-max: 1280px;
  --section-padding: 5rem;
  --section-padding-mobile: 3rem;

  /* Animation Easing */
  --ease-smooth: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  --ease-out: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);
  --ease-spring: cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);

  /* Animation Duration */
  --duration-fast: 150ms;
  --duration-normal: 300ms;
  --duration-slow: 500ms;

  /* Breakpoints */
  --breakpoint-sm: 640px;
  --breakpoint-md: 768px;
  --breakpoint-lg: 1024px;
  --breakpoint-xl: 1280px;
}

/* Base styles */
body {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  color: var(--color-neutral-800);
  background-color: white;
}

/* Focus visible for accessibility */
:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-sakura-500);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
```

Use the Edit tool to update the file.

